You're obviously talking about soloing in pvp.. So what you're saying is before this patch, the only thing you could do in PvP is:<P>Melee types:<BR>Charm, send helpless melee at a big ugly red npc.<P>Caster types:<BR>Charm, send helpless caster at a big ugly red npc.<P>I dunno about the rest of the people reading your post, but that's what it looks like to me. <P>There are other things you can do as an enchanter.. our dots are ok (only use at the end of the duel, when you don't need to mes them anymore, keep whirl handy for healers).. some nukes are resisted more than others.  I have bad luck with Anarchy, so I use other ones. You have plenty of time to decide which ones to use with mes.<P>Eldriash
