<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
heh, so we lost charm and we lost fear... why is everyone so pissed off?<P>Strategy against melee types in their big heavy armor... pet, dots, and weakening debuffs sounds good to me... c'mon, sapping about 60-80 pts of str, encumbering them, watching their Agi and thus movement speed/ac fall isn't good enough?  heck, I've made warriors motionless (just for fun and testing) doing this...<P>And I do believe we enchanters still get int debuffs at higher levels plus a mana drain spell... top it of we can mesmerize then med up for 20 seconds to keep up on mana... combine that at higher levels with clarity and we are not too bad off.<P>One final point... I believe we're the only class that can increase our attack speeds while decreasing our opponents, effectively doubling our attack rates.<P>So, for those ticked off the we can't take control away from another character and MAKE them commit suicide, look to your other abilities... and if you can't do that, do what most PKers do... just look for someone 4 levels below you almost dead that you can kill in one shot. :p<P>------------------<BR>Kithra Of Rallos Zek<BR>Enchanter and Craftsman<BR>of Freeport
